item.title: Dieing :O
item.dc:creator: @The_Dark_Abbys The Dark Abbys
item.description:
@The_Dark_Abbys wrote:

Hey there,

Your problem is that there is more than one way of dying,

for example you may only have changed where you go when an npc kills you

but still have not fixed what happens when a player kills you

I suggest searching for old coords and everytime u see them replace with new ones

That way you should always go to the spot you want

(Make sure you close runserver, then save, then compile, then run)

Good luck,
—The Dark Abbys—
